com.complexible.stardog.repair

Interface RepairPlan

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Iterable<com.complexible.stardog.api.update.UpdateOperation>, com.complexible.stardog.api.update.UpdateSequence

    public interface RepairPlan
extends com.complexible.stardog.api.update.UpdateSequence
    A specialization of UpdateSequence such that executing this update sequence will fix a set of conflicts. Each update operation in a repair plan corresponds to one OWL axiom.
    Since:
    2.3
    Version:
    2.3
    Author:
    Evren Sirin
